WEBVTT



00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:10.144
The ancient old city of Jerusalem is less than a square kilometer in size,

00:00:09.856 --> 00:00:17.536
but squeezed into its four quarters are more than forty thousand christians, jews, muslims and armenians.

00:00:17.344 --> 00:00:19.520
Who all call this home.

00:00:19.936 --> 00:00:28.864
Israel's National Emergency Rescue Service, Magan David Adom, has a big challenge reaching those who need urgent help.

00:00:28.672 --> 00:00:34.944
Because no ambulance can negotiate the narrow streets and stairs in much of the city.

00:00:35.328 --> 00:00:40.800
Mda has met the challenge with a specially designed all-terrain vehicle.

00:00:40.608 --> 00:00:43.616
Affectionately known as a mule.

00:00:43.552 --> 00:00:47.904
To bring emergency aid and transport to everyone in need.

00:00:48.864 --> 00:00:53.440
The mule currently in use has been working around the clock for six years.

00:00:53.088 --> 00:00:56.096
And is nearing the end of its mechanical life.

00:00:56.672 --> 00:00:59.008
That's why we're a Jerusalem channel.

00:00:58.848 --> 00:01:02.848
A launching a humanitarian appeal for 2021.

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:06.304
to raise the funds for a new rescue mule.

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:10.912
Our target is $37,150.

00:01:10.688 --> 00:01:14.624
Or in pounds, that's 27,300.

00:01:14.432 --> 00:01:17.600
In euros, 30,200.

00:01:17.792 --> 00:01:20.480
So, if you'd like to bless Israel,

00:01:20.384 --> 00:01:24.768
And in a practical way support all the families of the old city.

00:01:24.672 --> 00:01:26.816
Please consider making a gift.

00:01:26.528 --> 00:01:28.320
Through our website

00:01:28.256 --> 00:01:31.040
Mobile app or by mail.

00:01:31.392 --> 00:01:32.608
Thank you!
